'''亚当·理查德·莱格兹丁斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Adam Richard Legzdins'''}}，{{bd|1986年|11月28日|catIdx=Legzdins, Adam}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[守門員_(足球)|守門員]]，現時效力[[蘇格蘭足球超级联赛|蘇超]]球會[[邓迪足球俱乐部|邓迪]]。

==球會生涯==
莱格兹丁斯出身自[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]青訓系統，在2005年被外借到[[英格蘭足球議會北部聯賽|英議聯北部聯賽]]的[[阿尔费登镇足球俱乐部|阿尔费登镇]]參賽，期間共上場4次。之後他被外借至[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|全國聯]]的[[哈利法哈斯鎮足球會|哈利法哈斯鎮]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/halifax_town/4417624.stm |title=Shaymen seal swoop for Legzdins |publisher=BBC Sport |date=8 November 2005 |accessdate=5 January 2008 |archive-date=2005-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051124230337/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/halifax_town/4417624.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，共上場11次。

[[File:AdamLegzdins_cropped.jpg|thumb]]

2006年夏天，莱格兹丁斯簽下首份職業合約，為期一年。2006/07賽季初，因於球隊一號守門員[[迈克·泰勒|迈克·泰勒]]受傷，他獲發球衣號碼並在英冠對[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]的比賽擔任替補<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10412~35971,00.html |title=Adam Legzdins |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514131236/http://www.blues.premiumtv.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10412~35971,00.html |archivedate=2008-05-14 |accessdate=2015-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年10月，他被外借到[[奥尔德姆足球俱乐部|奥尔德姆]]擔任替補守門員，只在[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]上場一次<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/o/oldham_athletic/6181952.stm |title=Oldham extend Legzdins' loan deal |publisher=BBC Sport |date=24 November 2006 |accessdate=5 January 2008}}</ref>。之後外借到[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|马科斯菲尔德]]，但外借期間並沒有任何上場時間。

2007年夏天，球會延長了他的合約一年<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/wright-rejects-new-blues-deal-42583 |title=Wright rejects new Blues deal |author=Tattum, Colin |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=5 July 2007 |accessdate=12 August 2015 |archive-date=2016-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128104132/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/wright-rejects-new-blues-deal-42583 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並外借到[[哈利法哈斯鎮足球會|哈利法哈斯鎮]]三個月<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/halifax_town/7023535.stm |title=Halifax bag Birmingham goalkeeper |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2 October 2007 |accessdate=5 January 2008}}</ref>。2008年1月，莱格兹丁斯的外借期延長至季末<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/halifax_town/7172210.stm |title=Pair end spell with Halifax Town |publisher=BBC Sport |date=4 January 2008 |accessdate=4 June 2010 |archive-date=2017-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907220719/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/halifax_town/7172210.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年6月9日，他簽約加盟[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克鲁足球俱乐部]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/crewe_alexandra/7443799.stm |title=Crewe confirm signing of Legzdins |publisher=BBC Sport |date=9 June 2008 |accessdate=9 June 2008}}</ref>。

2009年8月11日，莱格兹丁斯首次代表克魯上場參賽[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]賽事以2-1敗給[[黑池足球會|黑池]]<ref>{{cite news 
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/crewe_alexandra/8197840.stm |title=Legzdins eager for games at Crewe |publisher=BBC Sport |date=13 August 2009 |accessdate=23 August 2009}}</ref>，8月22日首次在聯賽上場並以1-0主場擊敗[[靴尔福特联足球俱乐部|靴尔福特联]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.crewealex.net/page/MatchReport/0,,10414~47343,00.html |title=Crewe vs Hereford |publisher=Crewe Alexandra F.C |date=22 August 2009 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090826171221/http://www.crewealex.net/page/MatchReport/0,,10414~47343,00.html |archivedate=2009-08-26 |accessdate=2015-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===保顿艾尔宾===
2010年5月，莱格兹丁斯拒絕了克魯的一年合約，在7月1日與英乙的[[保顿艾尔宾足球俱乐部|保顿艾尔宾]]簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/crewe_alexandra/8703615.stm |title=Adam Legzdins turns down offer from Crewe Alexandra |publisher=BBC Sport |date=25 May 2010 |accessdate=4 June 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burton_albion/8779568.stm |title=Burton Albion swoop for goalkeeper Adam Legzdins |publisher=BBC Sport |date=1 July 2010 |accessdate=1 July 2010}}</ref>。2010年8月7日對[[牛津联足球俱乐部|牛津联]]的處子戰，以0-0力保清白之身<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10950~52650,00.html |title=Burton vs Oxford United |publisher=Burton Albion F.C. |date=7 August 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319005512/http://www.burtonalbionfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10950~52650,00.html |archivedate=2012-03-19 |accessdate=2015-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。莱格兹丁斯出戰了2010/11賽季所有聯賽，並當選為球迷選出和球員選出的年度最佳球員<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/13294146.stm |title=Adam Legzdins wins Burton Albion awards double |publisher=BBC Sport |date=5 May 2011 |accessdate=3 June 2011}}</ref>。

===德比郡===
2011年6月29日，保顿艾尔宾與[[德比郡足球俱乐部|德比郡]]在莱格兹丁斯轉會一事上達成共識<ref name="DCFC Move">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/13960105.stm|title=Derby County sign Adam Legzdins from Burton Albion|publisher=BBC Sport |date=1 July 2011|accessdate=29 June 2011}}</ref>，莱格兹丁斯在7月1日轉會至德比群並簽約三年。他在德比郡的首戰是作客對[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]，因守門員[[法蘭·費丁|法蘭·費丁]]開場1分鐘後因紅牌離場而獲得上場機會<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/14864055.stm |title=Nottm Forest 1–2 Derby |publisher=BBC Sport |date=17 September 2011 |accessdate=17 September 2011}}</ref>。2012年3月20日，莱格兹丁斯緊急外借到舊東家保顿艾尔宾<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17443314 |title=Burton bring back Derby County goalkeeper Adam Legzdins |publisher=BBC Sport |date=20 March 2012 |accessdate=20 March 2012 |archive-date=2013-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016184327/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17443314 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但上場1次後因傷而在4月17日回到德比郡<ref>{{cite news |url=http://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/17042012/63/legzdins-rams.html |title=Legzdins back with Rams |publisher=Eurosport Yahoo |date=17 April 2012 |accessdate=17 April 2012 |archive-date=2012-07-26 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120726233537/http://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/17042012/63/legzdins-rams.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012/13球季，莱格兹丁斯依舊是二號守門員。10月，由於費丁受傷，因此他回到先發陣容<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thisisderbyshire.co.uk/Derby-County-goalkeeper-Adam-Legzdins-set-stay/story-17402691-detail/story.html |title=Derby County goalkeeper Adam Legzdins set to stay at number one spot when Birmingham City visit Pride Park Stadium |first=Steve |last=Nicholson |newspaper=Derby Telegraph |date=23 November 2012 |accessdate=12 August 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923224745/http://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/Derby-County-goalkeeper-Adam-Legzdins-set-stay/story-17402691-detail/story.html |archivedate=2015年9月23日 }}</ref>。期間教練[[尼祖·哥洛夫|尼祖·哥洛夫]]對莱格兹丁斯的表現印象深刻，尤其是2-0擊敗[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔城]]一戰終止球隊連續7戰失球及4連敗劣勢<ref name="briscgame">{{cite news |url=http://www.thisisderbyshire.co.uk/Keeper-Adam-Legzdins-deserved-clean-sheet-seven/story-17608832-detail/story.html |title=Keeper Adam Legzdins deserved first clean sheet in seven, says boss |newspaper=Derby Telegraph |date=17 December 2012 |accessdate=12 August 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519150242/http://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/Keeper-Adam-Legzdins-deserved-clean-sheet-seven/story-17608832-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014年5月19日 }}</ref>。2013年3月，由於哥洛夫認為對[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]的比賽需要用上經驗豐富的費丁，因此莱格兹丁斯的連續30場比陣紀錄終止，而球隊最終以2-1取勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thisisderbyshire.co.uk/Centre-halves-won-Leicester-game-says-Derby/story-18449567-detail/story.html |title=Centre-halves 'won us the Leicester game,' says Derby County's Nigel Clough |newspaper=Derby Telegraph |date=18 March 2013 |accessdate=12 August 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526021548/http://www.thisisderbyshire.co.uk/Centre-halves-won-Leicester-game-says-Derby/story-18449567-detail/story.html |archivedate=2013年5月26日 }}</ref>。五星期後，費丁因為對彼德堡期間職業犯規被逐，莱格兹丁斯又回到場上比賽並參加賽案餘下兩場比賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22133302 |publisher=BBC Sport |title=Derby 3–1 Peterborough |date=20 April 2013 |accessdate=12 August 2015 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017140651/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22133302 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，整個賽季他共上場33次。2014年5月，德比郡從[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|伯恩利]]簽下守門員[[李·格兰特_(1983年出生足球運動員)|李·格兰特]]，莱格兹丁斯被掛牌轉會<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/Rams-listen-offers-Fielding-Legzdins/story-18914541-detail/story.html |newspaper=Derby Telegraph |first=Steve |last=Nicholson |title=Rams will listen to offers for Fielding and Legzdins |date=8 May 2013 |accessdate=12 August 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924002512/http://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/Rams-listen-offers-Fielding-Legzdins/story-18914541-detail/story.html |archivedate=2015年9月24日 }}</ref>。

===莱顿东方===
2014年6月13日，他與英甲球會[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|莱顿东方]]簽下兩年合約<ref>{{cite news |title=Adam Legzdins: Leyton Orient sign Derby County goalkeeper |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27835791 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=13 June 2014 |accessdate=13 June 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810213841/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27835791 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於他整個賽季因傷患而缺乏上場機會，雙方在2015年6月1日協議解約<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32962766 |title=Adam Legzdins: Leyton Orient terminate keeper's contract |date=1 June 2015 |accessdate=1 June 2015 |publisher=BBC Sport |archive-date=2015-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601210705/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32962766 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===伯明翰城===
莱格兹丁斯在2015年6月7日回到伯明翰城並簽約兩年，另加一年選擇權<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33298887 |title=Adam Legzdins: Birmingham City sign goalkeeper |publisher=BBC Sport |date=27 June 2015 |accessdate=27 June 2015 |archive-date=2015-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708040226/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33298887 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在聯賽盃2-1擊敗[[布里斯托尔流浪者足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔流浪者]]的比賽上演首秀。

